    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline to deliver linear power through the 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive fluid flush and inspection of the throttle actuators to ensure peak operational integrity. This example retains its mechanical purity and provides a visceral driving experience for the discerning enthusiast looking for a solid driver's car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
