    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. This car has been a reliable daily driver, consistently serviced at scheduled intervals with a full folder of records included. Mechanically, it is in robust shape; the engine runs quietly, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest wear that reflects its history on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a clean and comfortable sanctuary. The upholstery is well-preserved with minimal creasing, and all electronic features, including the navigation system and heated seats, function perfectly. We recently fitted a fresh set of all-season tires and performed a full fluid flush, ensuring this car is turn-key ready for its next owner. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a high-quality, dependable vehicle without the showroom-new price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
